metadata.name: High Noon
metadata.description:
This image was captured on a mid-day drive through Badlands National Park. I used a 10 stop neutral density filter to combat the harsh afternoon light and create this dramatic black and white scene

A percentage of every sale will be donated to the Badlands National Park Conservancy for ongoing conservation efforts. A second donation will be made to Give Back to Nature

7360 × 4912
300dpi
